spanGrp.span: [clapping] [xx] Nasraldeen is going to speak about the cattle-breeding in the Tabaq community

NHK talks about the importance of cattle-breeding in the Tabaq community. In addition he adds information about the other domestic animals, as there are goats and sheep, horses and camels. He remembers that formerly pigs played a role as well.
Panasonic Lumix DMC-GH2K (set to AVCHD(1080i), FSH), plus external stereo microphone (Rode Stereo VideoMic) & windshield
Zoom H4n, internal microphone (set to WAV, 44.1Hz/16bit) & windshield
